node.text:
Hi! MY FIRST EVER IGTV ! My friends and I decided to visit LA and we went out the day before so we decided to stay inside and this is what our night consisted of... HAHA! They had been begging to play hide and seek that whole week and I was NOT feeling it 😭 If you’d like more videos like this, vote on the poll on my Instagram story or comment below! 
Subscribe to Youtube.com/MsAaliyahJay for more videos + vlogs

Follow @Jay_lindo + @iamalexpatrick 
Filmed by @alrdysuccessful

node.title: A NIGHT INSIDE WITH MY FRIENDS

node.text:
When it’s pay day 🤑💚
New items I get to add to my closet, thanks to @luxurysnob . I’ve been looking all over for these exact items and they found it for me! 🙏🏽 I’ve been thinking about getting rid of some of my old designer items 🤔 Would you guys buy them if I listed them on @luxurysnob? Let me know! Can’t wait to wear these pieces! ✨🤍

node.text: A man who listens 💕 My dream was to always go to a farm and feed baby goats (iykyk lol) and he surprised me and made this happen. I can’t thank you enough for listening and paying attention to my wants & my needs! You truly DO love me so much and I thank you for trying to be the best you can be, even when it feels impossible for us together & separately. I cried like an entire baby you guys….. 🥲 He just pays attention to me so much I truly can’t believe he makes everything I say I want, come true! It’s like being in a fairytale 🪄🥺😍🥲 I love you in all forms! I love this for us! 💍 ❤️ 😘@wizardkelly
